{"tid":1702099,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【知法犯法】「警察是強姦犯」 墨西哥城數百人抗議警察性侵婦女","createTime":"2019-11-09T13:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T14:35:38.000Z","uid":247494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8848e6dbd0d7d1ec6c145ecc5d0a72a8394a14dc","tid":1702099,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:54:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190817/59942077\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190817%2F59942077&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSppSOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=7ffc17b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190817%2F59942077&h=d3aaade2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190817/59942077</a><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥首都墨西哥城昨日舉行了一場「閃粉示威」，數百名婦女在市中心遊行，抗議過去有多宗警察涉性侵婦女的事件。<br />\n<br />\n示威者是不滿當局對調查這些強姦案的進度緩慢，她們在身上噴上粉紅色顏料，或撒開粉紅色粉末，大叫「警察是強姦犯」、「友人保護我，而不是警方」等口號。日前她們到政府辦公室外抗議，但官員拒絕跟她們會面，所以示威者破壞辦公室。墨西哥城市長譴責示威者，又表示要調查示威者的破壞舉動，激起民憤。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">示威者在昨日的抗議行動中，破壞了一個巴士站、打破玻璃或毀壞閘門，遊行人士後來去到警署，用雜物打破玻璃窗並在二樓放火，市內的象徵性建築獨立紀念柱（Independence Monument）的底部石座，亦被人塗鴉表達不滿。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n本周一名輔警涉嫌在博物館強暴一名年輕女職員被起訴，本月初也有多名警員，被一名女子控告在警車內企圖強暴她。由於早前有示威者在墨西哥城警察總長身上淋上粉紅閃粉，因此今次示威被稱為「閃粉示威」。<br />\n<br />\n警方表現克制，未有向示威者施放催淚彈。而市長再次譴責暴力，但她強調不會武力鎮壓示威，而暴力示威也不會阻止雙方對話的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家千萬不要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5855bfe88c1b5572b04470953c2d1bda790c87","tid":1702099,"uid":293227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:58:41.000Z","msg":"結界師<br />\n<br />\n一個建築物3級大火<br />\n<br />\n死一兩隻狗<br />\n<br />\n這是必會出現的"},{"pid":"40c2b5d885a17bb690b068afa7039231d8a72815","tid":1702099,"uid":14148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:01:46.000Z","msg":"香港班婦團收撚皮啦 <br />\n有晒料連譴責都冇句"},{"pid":"b3d94a8b573cc10a3e136801bda0d47a167a642b","tid":1702099,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:03:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">NOS ESTAN MATANDO Y T&Uacute; NO HACES NADA！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38944f7604e274716c45d3e63b076ba0a6ab2db2","tid":1702099,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:07:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e75184a829abd421fc9096b65a119feae4f705c4","tid":1702099,"uid":36378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38779a20174b5784ffd1df9b39d1e11ea2cbbb7b","tid":1702099,"uid":198097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:25:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>強姦就強姦, 輪姦就輪姦, 非禮就非禮, 性乜撚侵, 多魚.</strong></span>"},{"pid":"e05327c890b3d46df91d2d544777eaad4701f094","tid":1702099,"uid":256192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"